title: Comfortable Renovated 3 Br/2Ba Apt Homes @Fountain Villas
posting_body: ['The beautiful community of Fountain Park and Fountain Villas has great unit and amenities.', 'Our community is located in a quiet neighborhood and in a beautiful area of Canoga Park.', 'Close to freeways, shopping center, restaurants, parks and schools.', 'Community Amenities:', '• Walk-In Closets', '• Pet Friendly Community with Manicured Dog Run', '• Close to Plenty of Hiking Trails', '• Large, Refreshing Swimming Pool', '• Easy Access to the 118 and 101 Freeways and the Metro Stations', '• Close to Warner Center, Fine Dining and, Shopping', '• Assigned Parking', '• Fitness Center', '• \u200bGated Community \u200b', '• Great Location', '• On-Site Laundry Facility', '• Professional On-Site Maintenance', 'Apartment Amenities:', '• Central Heat and Air', '• Additional Private Storage', '• Separate Dining', '• Dishwasher', '• Extra Storage', '• Garbage Disposal', '• Microwave*', '• Mirrored Wardrobe Doors*', '• Pantry', '• Private Patio or Balcony', '• Refrigerator*', "Certain floor plans may have different amenities depending on when they were updated, what building they're in, etc.", 'To tour our floor plans and see what amenities may be available, please call us at', 'show contact info', ';', 'please do NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers.']
